gw.entity

Interface ITypeList<T extends TypeKey>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, IEnhanceableType, com.guidewire.pl.system.entity.external.IExternalType, IFileBasedType, IFileRepositoryBasedType, IHasJavaClass, IJavaBackedType, IJavaBackedTypeData, IType, java.io.Serializable

    public interface ITypeList<T extends TypeKey>
extends IJavaBackedType, java.lang.Comparable, com.guidewire.pl.system.entity.external.IExternalType, IEnhanceableType, IFileRepositoryBasedType, IFileBasedType
    Version:
    May 20, 2002 3:48:53 PM

    The TypeList serves as a representation of an entire typelist, containing a TypeKey object for each of the values that members of this list can take. It also provides lookups for associated TypeKeys based on id, code, and name.

    Author:
    mshaw
